e MP\nphenomenon is the same, regardless of cluster age and host galaxy. As such,\nthese young clusters offer some of the strictest tests for theories on the\norigin of MPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Sep 2020 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
