imizing the reconstruction errors in each layer. Extensive\nexperiments on several real databases demonstrate that our DS2CF-Net can obtain\nstate-of-the-art performance for representation learning and clustering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2020 13:10:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 09:08:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
